window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Available for the first time in a single, accessible volume.</b></p> <p>The stakes have never been higher. After making an inadvertent sacrifice in an abandoned temple, a college professor and his busty graduate assistant become wrapped up in a mad God's game. The prize: the future of humanity.</p> <p>Lucas must navigate level after level as he ascends to the Celestial throne. Along the way, he'll pick up a coterie of magical maidens to assist him on his quest. As he levels up his abilities, he will confront his deepest fear—losing the ones he loves most.</p>"; 
